A few weeks back, Gracious Amani, the talented girl from Githurai took the Internet by storm singing to Alicia Keys'song ‘Girl on Fire’. The American superstar was wowed like the rest of the world and shared the video on Instagram and wrote: "Look at this beautiful soul, shine!" Amani was first recorded by a visiting tourist, Britt Chantel, who was equally blown away by her melodious voice. Now, the 13-year old has dropped her first single titled 'Sitasahau'. Read about Amani's journey to this release